Simulation - governs simulation flow, coordinates bodies, forces, controllers etc

Integrator - translates force inputs and updates positional states

Kinematics/Contraints - determines how rigid bodies can move in the simulation

DynamicalSystem - Generates the aggregate force, same as state space model

Controller - applies control input that contributes to forward update of state

Renderer - takes positional states of rigid bodies and outputs them to viewer at certain rate

Logger - outputs data, timestamps for visualization, debugging , etc


